texts.content: {"text":"1. Haa. Miym.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,13]}]}

{"text":"2. Kitob tushirilishi g'olib va hikmatli \nAlloh tarafidandir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,61]}]}

{"text":"3. Osmonlaru yerni hamda ular o`rtasidagi narsalarni faqat haq va belgilangan muddat ila yaratdik. \nKofirlar bo`lsa, o`zlari ogohlantirilgan narsadan \nyuz o`giruvchilardir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,172]}]}

{"text":"4. Sen: «Allohdan o`zga sig`inayotgan narsalaringizning xabarini bering-chi, menga \nko`rsating-chi, ular yerdan nimani yaratdilar? \nYoki osmonlarni (yaratishda) ishtiroklari bormi? ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,181]}]}

{"text":"Agar rostgo`y bo`lsalaringiz, \nmenga bu(Qur'on)dan oldingi kitobni yoki ilmiy \nbir belgini (dalilni) keltiring», deb ayt.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,121]}]}

{"text":"5. Allohni qo`yib, qiyomat kunigacha \nduosini mustajob qilolmaydiganlarga iltijo etadiganlardan ham adashganroqlar bormi?! \nHolbuki, u(but)lar ularning duosidan g`ofildirlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,174]}]}

{"text":"6. Odamlar mahsharga to`planganda, o`sha(but)lar ularga dushman bo`lurlar va ibodatlariga ham munkir bo`lurlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,111]}]}

{"text":"7. Qachonki ularga ravshan oyatlarimiz tilovat qilinsa, kufr keltirganlar Haq (Qur'on) ularga kelgandayoq, bu ochiq-oydin sehrdir, derlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,138]}]}

{"text":"8. Balki, u(Qur'on)ni o`zi to`qib olgan, ham derlar. 
Sen: «Agar uni to`qib olgan bo`lsam, Allohdan 
(keladigan) biror narsani mendan qaytarishga qodir emassiz. U zotning O`zi u(kitob) haqida siz 
sho`ng`iyotgan narsalarni yaxshi biluvchidir. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,243]}]}

{"text":"Men bilan sizning o`rtangizda \nguvohlikka Uning O`zi kifoyadir. \nVa U kechiruvchi ham rahimli Zotdir», deb ayt.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,111]}]}

{"text":"9. Sen: «Men birinchi Payg`ambar emasman, 
menga va sizlarga nima qilinishini bilmasman. 
Faqat, o`zimga vahiy qilinayotgan 
narsagagina ergashurman. 
Men ochiq-oydin ogohlantiruvchiman, xolos», deb ayt.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,203]}]}

{"text":"10. Sen: «Ayting-chi, agar u (Qur'on) Allohdan bo`lsa-yu, siz unga kufr keltirsangiz va holbuki, Bani Isroildan bir guvoh u(Qur'on)ga o`xshash narsaga guvohlik berib, iymon keltirib turibdi, siz esa, kibru havo qilyapsiz. Albatta, Alloh zolim qavmlarni hidoyat qilmas», deb ayt.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,278]}]}

{"text":"11. Kufr keltirganlar iymon keltirganlarga: \n«Agar u (Qur'on) yaxshilik bo`lganida, unga bizdan avval bormasdilar», dedilar. U(Qur'on)dan hidoyat topishmagach, bu — qadimgi uydirmadir, derlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,192]}]}

{"text":"12. U(Qur'on)dan oldin Musoning \nkitobi yo`l boshlovchi va rahmat edi. \nBu (Qur'on) esa, arab tilidagi, tasdiqlovchi, zulm qiluvchilarni ogohlantirish uchun va yaxshilarga bashorat kitobidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,191]}]}

{"text":"13. Albatta «Robbimiz Allohdir» degan, \nso`ngra bunda mustaqiym turganlarga \nxavf yo`qdir va ular xafa ham bo`lmaslar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,118]}]}

{"text":"14. Ana o`shalar jannat egalaridir, \nqilgan amallari mukofotiga unda abadiy qolurlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,85]}]}

{"text":"15. Biz insonni ota-onasiga yaxshilik qilishga buyurdik. Onasi unga qiynalib homilador bo`ldi va \nuni qiynalib tug`di. Va uning homilasi va \nko`krakdan ajratishi o`ttiz oydir. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,176]}]}

{"text":"Toki, u kamolga yetib, qirq yoshga kirganida: 
«Robbim, O`zing menga va ota-onamga bergan 
ne'matlaringga shukr qilishimga va Sen rozi 
bo`lgan solih(ish)ni qilishimga ilhom bergin. 
Va mening zurriyotlarimni ham solihlardan qilgin. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,233]}]}

{"text":"Albatta, men tavba qildim va albatta, \nmen musulmonlardanman», dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,68]}]}

{"text":"16. Ana o`shalarning eng yaxshi amallarini 
qabul qilib, yomonliklarini o`tib yuborurmiz. 
Ular jannat egalaridandir. 
Ularga berilgan haq va'da shuldir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,153]}]}

{"text":"17. Ota-onasiga: «Uff sizlarga, (qabrdan) chiqarilishimning va'dasini berayapsizlarmi?! Mendan avval ham asrlar o`tgan-ku!» – degan kishiga, Allohdan madad so`ragan holda, ular: «Holingga voy bo`lgur, iymon keltir, albatta, Allohning va'dasi haqdir», dedilar. \nU bo`lsa: «Bu o`tganlarning afsonalari, xolos», der.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,313]}]}

{"text":"18. Ana o`shalarga o`zlaridan avval o`tgan jin va ins ummatlari qatorida (azob) so`zi haq bo`lgandir. Albatta, ular ziyon ko`ruvchilardan bo`ldilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,148]}]}

{"text":"19. Har birlariga qilgan amallariga yarasha darajalar bordir. Va ularga amallarining (mukofot yoki jazosi) to`liq berilur va ularga zulm qilinmas.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,146]}]}

{"text":"20. Kufr keltirganlar do`zaxga ko`ndalang \nqilingan kunda (ularga): «Hayoti dunyodayoq \nhuzur-halovatingizni ketkazib, mazasini tatib bo`lgansiz. Bugungi kunda yer yuzida nohaq kibru havo va fisqu fasod qilganingiz uchun xorlik azobi ila jazolanursiz», deyilur.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,261]}]}

{"text":"21. O`z qavmini qum tepaliklarda ogohlantirgan \nOdning birodarini esla! Va holbuki, undan avval ham, keyin ham ogohlantiruvchilar o`tgan. «U zotdan \no`zgaga ibodat qilmanglar, albatta, men ulug` kunda boshingizga tushadigan azobdan qo`rqurman, (dedi)».","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,252]}]}

{"text":"22. Ular: «Bizni xudolarimizdan ozdirishga keldingmi? Agar rostgo`ylardan bo`lsang, bizga va'da qilayotgan narsangni keltir», dedilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,134]}]}

{"text":"23. U: «Albatta, ilm Allohning huzuridadir. \nMen nima bilan yuborilgan bo`lsam, \nshuni yetkazmoqdaman. Lekin sizlarning johil qavmligingizni ko`rib turibman», dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,164]}]}

{"text":"24. U(azob)ning vodiylari tomon ko`ndalang 
bo`lib yurganini ko`rishganda, bu ko`ndalang 
bo`luvchi bizga yomg`ir yog`dirur, deyishdi. 
Yo`q! Bu, o`zingiz orziqib so`ragan narsa, 
alamli azobi bor bo`rondir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,207]}]}

{"text":"25. U, Robbisining amri ila har bir narsani vayron qilur. Bas, maskanlaridan boshqa narsa ko`rinmay qoldi. Jinoyatchi qavmlarni shundoq jazolarmiz.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,147]}]}

{"text":"26. Va, darhaqiqat, \nBiz ularga sizga bermagan imkonlarni bergan edik. Hamda quloq, ko`z va qalblar ato etdik. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,111]}]}

{"text":"Bas, na quloqlari, na ko`zlari va na qalblari ularga hech bir foyda bermadi. Chunki, ular Allohning oyatlarini inkor qilgan edilar. Bas, ularni o`zlari masxara qilgan narsa (azob) o`rab oldi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,191]}]}

{"text":"27. Haqiqatan, atrofingizdagi shahar-qishloqlarni halokatga uchratdik va shoyadki, o`zlariga qaytsalar, deb hujjat-dalillarni bayon qildik.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,139]}]}

{"text":"28. Qani endi, Allohni qo`yib, U zotga yaqinlashtiruvchi deb tutingan «xudolari» ularga yordam bersalar edi. \nYo`q! Ular g`oyib bo`ldilar. \nVa bu ularning uydirma hamda to`qigan bo`htonlaridir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,193]}]}

{"text":"29. Va sen tomon bir guruh jinlarni Qur'on eshitishga burganimizni esla. U(Qur'on eshitish)ga hozir \nbo`lganlarida: «Jim, quloq osinglar!» – dedilar. Qachonki, qiroat oxirlaganda, o`z qavmlariga ogohlantiruvchi bo`lib qaytdilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,228]}]}

{"text":"30. Ular: «Ey qavmimiz! 
Biz Musodan keyin tushirilgan, o`zidan avvalgi 
narsa(kitoblar)ni tasdiqlovchi, haq(din)ga va 
to`g`ri yo`lga hidoyat qiluvchi kitobni eshitdik.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,169]}]}

{"text":"31. Ey qavmimiz, Allohning da'vatchisiga javob bering va Unga iymon keltiring. U sizlarning gunohlaringizni mag`firat qilar va alamli azobdan saqlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,149]}]}

{"text":"32. Kimki, Allohning da'vatchisini qabul qilmasa, bas, u yer yuzida qochib qutula oluvchi emasdir va unga U zotdan o`zga valiylar ham yo`qdir. Ana o`shalar ochiq-oydin zalolatdadir», dedilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,191]}]}

{"text":"33. Ular osmonlaru yerni yaratgan va ularni yaratishda behol bo`lmagan Alloh o`liklarni ham tiriltirishga qodir ekanini anglab yetmadilarmi? \nZero, U zot har bir narsaga qodirdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,179]}]}

{"text":"34. Kufr keltirganlar do`zaxga ko`ndalang 
qilingan kunda: «Bu, haq emasmi?!» (deyilur). 
Ular: «Robbimizga qasamki, xuddi shundoq», dedilar. 
«Bas, kufr keltirganingiz uchun azobni tortinglar», dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,200]}]}

{"text":"35. Bas, azmu matonat sohibi bo`lgan \nPayg`ambarlar sabr qilgandek, sabr qil, \nularga (azob yetishiga) shoshilma! ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,114]}]}

{"text":"Ular va'da qilingan narsani ko`rganlarida \nxuddi (bu dunyoda) kunduzdan bir lahzagina turganga o`xsharlar. Bu yetkazishdir! \nBas, faqat fosiq qavmlargina halok qilinur, xolos!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,175]}]}

{"text":"حمٓ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,3]}]}

{"text":"تَنزِيلُ ٱلْكِتَٰبِ مِنَ ٱللَّهِ ٱلْعَزِيزِ ٱلْحَكِيمِ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,54]}]}

{"text":"مَا خَلَقْنَا ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضَ وَمَا بَيْنَهُمَآ إِلَّا بِٱلْحَقِّ وَأَجَلٍۢ مُّسَمًّۭى ۚ \nوَٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ عَمَّآ أُنذِرُوا۟ مُعْرِضُونَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,153]}]}

{"text":"قُلْ أَرَءَيْتُم مَّا تَدْعُونَ مِن دُونِ ٱللَّهِ أَرُونِى مَاذَا \nخَلَقُوا۟ مِنَ ٱلْأَرْضِ أَمْ لَهُمْ شِرْكٌۭ فِى ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ ۖ ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,132]}]}

{"text":"ٱئْتُونِى بِكِتَٰبٍۢ مِّن قَبْلِ هَٰذَآ أَوْ أَثَٰرَةٍۢ مِّنْ عِلْمٍ إِن كُنتُمْ صَٰدِقِينَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,92]}]}

{"text":"وَمَنْ أَضَلُّ مِمَّن يَدْعُوا۟ مِن دُونِ ٱللَّهِ مَن لَّا يَسْتَجِيبُ لَهُۥٓ \nإِلَىٰ يَوْمِ ٱلْقِيَٰمَةِ وَهُمْ عَن دُعَآئِهِمْ غَٰفِلُونَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,140]}]}

{"text":"وَإِذَا حُشِرَ ٱلنَّاسُ كَانُوا۟ لَهُمْ أَعْدَآءًۭ وَكَانُوا۟ بِعِبَادَتِهِمْ كَٰفِرِينَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,89]}]}

{"text":"فَلَوْلَا نَصَرَهُمُ ٱلَّذِينَ ٱتَّخَذُوا۟ مِن دُونِ ٱللَّهِ قُرْبَانًا ءَالِهَةًۢ ۖ \nبَلْ ضَلُّوا۟ عَنْهُمْ ۚ وَذَٰلِكَ إِفْكُهُمْ وَمَا كَانُوا۟ يَفْتَرُونَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,158]}]}

{"text":"وَإِذْ صَرَفْنَآ إِلَيْكَ نَفَرًۭا مِّنَ ٱلْجِنِّ يَسْتَمِعُونَ ٱلْقُرْءَانَ فَلَمَّا حَضَرُوهُ \nقَالُوٓا۟ أَنصِتُوا۟ ۖ فَلَمَّا قُضِىَ وَلَّوْا۟ إِلَىٰ قَوْمِهِم مُّنذِرِينَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,175]}]}

{"text":"قَالُوا۟ يَٰقَوْمَنَآ إِنَّا سَمِعْنَا كِتَٰبًا أُنزِلَ مِنۢ بَعْدِ مُوسَىٰ \nمُصَدِّقًۭا لِّمَا بَيْنَ يَدَيْهِ يَهْدِىٓ إِلَى ٱلْحَقِّ وَإِلَىٰ طَرِيقٍۢ مُّسْتَقِيمٍۢ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,168]}]}

{"text":"يَٰقَوْمَنَآ أَجِيبُوا۟ دَاعِىَ ٱللَّهِ وَءَامِنُوا۟ بِهِۦ يَغْفِرْ لَكُم مِّن ذُنُوبِكُمْ \nوَيُجِرْكُم مِّنْ عَذَابٍ أَلِيمٍۢ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,127]}]}

{"text":"وَمَن لَّا يُجِبْ دَاعِىَ ٱللَّهِ فَلَيْسَ بِمُعْجِزٍۢ فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ وَلَيْسَ لَهُۥ مِن دُونِهِۦٓ أَوْلِيَآءُ ۚ \nأُو۟لَٰٓئِكَ فِى ضَلَٰلٍۢ مُّبِينٍ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,148]}]}

{"text":"أَوَلَمْ يَرَوْا۟ أَنَّ ٱللَّهَ ٱلَّذِى خَلَقَ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضَ وَلَمْ يَعْىَ بِخَلْقِهِنَّ بِقَٰدِرٍ \nعَلَىٰٓ أَن يُحْۦِىَ ٱلْمَوْتَىٰ ۚ بَلَىٰٓ إِنَّهُۥ عَلَىٰ كُلِّ شَىْءٍۢ قَدِيرٌۭ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,193]}]}

{"text":"وَيَوْمَ يُعْرَضُ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ عَلَى ٱلنَّارِ أَلَيْسَ هَٰذَا بِٱلْحَقِّ ۖ قَالُوا۟ بَلَىٰ وَرَبِّنَا ۚ\n قَالَ فَذُوقُوا۟ ٱلْعَذَابَ بِمَا كُنتُمْ تَكْفُرُونَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,165]}]}
